@OlaOlaD: I can´t read norsk, but it sounds like you may have a problem with the install ;). 
The install is quite simple, just extract the content of the zip file to your garmin directory, most likely it´s "c:\garmin", unless you changed it. Then have a look in the subfolder FAM_890 (c:\garmin\FAM_890 for example). There is a FAM_890.reg-file which contains data that needs to be added to your windows registry. But before double-clicking this file, you need to edit it, because it points at "c:\data\garmin\", which isn´t your path most likely. You´ll have to right-click on the reg-file and open it with a text editor like notepad. Simply adjust the six pathes that they match your directory structure. If "c:\garmin" is your mapsource folder, than simply delete the string "data\\" from each path line for example. Now you can double-click the reg-file and that should be all ;).
